{"tid":499420,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個睇完覺得好慘但係好好笑嘅新聞","createTime":"2017-12-14T19:00:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T05:23:53.000Z","uid":148093,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9285f1e803fdfc81c6c52a23148d1d9102c8b960","tid":499420,"uid":148093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T19:00:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/025958_a8093c18cb5b9065c4c3b027f0a0ed79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F025958_a8093c18cb5b9065c4c3b027f0a0ed79.jpg&h=8cd205d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/640pix/20050530/Article_ent/30ec5p73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20050530%2FArticle_ent%2F30ec5p73.jpg&h=a6ff30b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歌手王啟文把《老鼠愛大米》唱得街知巷聞，可惜他上周末獲邀到香港舉行簽唱會卻慘淡收場。王啟文不僅破了簽唱會Fans人數最少的紀錄，還有路人投以奇怪目光，結果他在免費送了5張唱片給路人後，取消了簽唱會。 <br />\n<br />\n　 <br />\n　王啟文上周赴港作為期4天的宣傳，活動命名為《超人氣王啟文簽唱會》，可惜現場不僅未見&ldquo;超人氣&rdquo;，甚至連一點人氣都沒有。5月29日，簽唱會現場入場人數只有20多人，而排隊找王啟文索取簽名的歌迷數目竟是&ldquo;零&rdquo;，場面出奇的冷清。直至他獻唱新歌《嫁給我吧》，圍觀者才逐漸增加。王啟文微笑地唱完4首歌，並在玩遊戲過程送出5張簽名CD後，便黯然離場，簽唱會在沒有歌迷索取簽名的情況下結束。"},{"pid":"8fe3dad5aba602cc27bc4c5f35e2954f79ec73fa","tid":499420,"uid":122892,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T19:02:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37b800ca00abf7f866934d9b3939fc80a439bec6","tid":499420,"uid":148093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T19:05:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/025958_a8093c18cb5b9065c4c3b027f0a0ed79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F025958_a8093c18cb5b9065c4c3b027f0a0ed79.jpg&h=8cd205d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia